The paper deals with data analysis of graphs using OLAP, which is a database-related topic, hence it is likely to belong to cs.DB. The proposed Structural Significance measure and iGraphCubing algorithm are related to graph theory and structural analysis, which fall under cs.SI and cs.DS. The paper also mentions evaluating the proposed ideas on real and synthetic data sets, which suggests the involvement of information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques.
